49static const char *program = "named-checkconf";
50
51static bool loadplugins = true;
52
53isc_log_t *logc = NULL;
54
55#define CHECK(r)\
56 do { \
57 result = (r); \
58 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) \
59 goto cleanup; \
60 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)

62/*% usage */
63ISC_PLATFORM_NORETURN_PRE static void
64usage(void) ISC_PLATFORM_NORETURN_POST;
65
66static void
67usage(void) {
68 fprintf(stderr, "usage: %s [-chjlvz] [-p [-x]] [-t directory] "
69 "[named.conf]\n", program);
70 exit(1);
71}

73/*% directory callback */
74static isc_result_t
75directory_callback(const char *clausename, const cfg_obj_t *obj, void *arg) {
76 isc_result_t result;
77 const char *directory;
78
79 REQUIRE(strcasecmp("directory", clausename) == 0);
80
81 UNUSED(arg);
82 UNUSED(clausename);
83
84 /*
85 * Change directory.
86 */
87 directory = cfg_obj_asstring(obj);
88 result = isc_dir_chdir(directory);
89 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
90 cfg_obj_log(obj, logc, ISC_LOG_ERROR,
91 "change directory to '%s' failed: %s\n",
92 directory, isc_result_totext(result));
93 return (result);
94 }
95
96 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
97}
98
99static bool
100get_maps(const cfg_obj_t **maps, const char *name, const cfg_obj_t **obj) {
101 int i;
102 for (i = 0;; i++) {
103 if (maps[i] == NULL)
104 return (false);
105 if (cfg_map_get(maps[i], name, obj) == ISC_R_SUCCESS)
106 return (true);
107 }
108}
109
110static bool
111get_checknames(const cfg_obj_t **maps, const cfg_obj_t **obj) {
112 const cfg_listelt_t *element;
113 const cfg_obj_t *checknames;
114 const cfg_obj_t *type;
115 const cfg_obj_t *value;
116 isc_result_t result;
117 int i;
118
119 for (i = 0;; i++) {
120 if (maps[i] == NULL)
121 return (false);
122 checknames = NULL;
123 result = cfg_map_get(maps[i], "check-names", &checknames);
124 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
125 continue;
126 if (checknames != NULL && !cfg_obj_islist(checknames)) {
127 *obj = checknames;
128 return (true);
129 }
130 for (element = cfg_list_first(checknames);
131 element != NULL;
132 element = cfg_list_next(element)) {
133 value = cfg_listelt_value(element);
134 type = cfg_tuple_get(value, "type");
135 if ((strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(type),
136 "primary") != 0) &&
137 (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(type),
138 "master") != 0))
139 {
140 continue;
141 }
142 *obj = cfg_tuple_get(value, "mode");
143 return (true);
144 }
145 }
146}
147
148static isc_result_t
149configure_hint(const char *zfile, const char *zclass, isc_mem_t *mctx) {
150 isc_result_t result;
151 dns_db_t *db = NULL;
152 dns_rdataclass_t rdclass;
153 isc_textregion_t r;
154
155 if (zfile == NULL)
156 return (ISC_R_FAILURE);
157
158 DE_CONST(zclass, r.base);
159 r.length = strlen(zclass);
160 result = dns_rdataclass_fromtext(&rdclass, &r);
161 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
162 return (result);
163
164 result = dns_rootns_create(mctx, rdclass, zfile, &db);
165 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
166 return (result);
167
168 dns_db_detach(&db);
169 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
170}

172/*% configure the zone */
173static isc_result_t
174configure_zone(const char *vclass, const char *view,
175 const cfg_obj_t *zconfig, const cfg_obj_t *vconfig,
176 const cfg_obj_t *config, isc_mem_t *mctx, bool list)
177{
178 int i = 0;
179 isc_result_t result;
180 const char *zclass;
181 const char *zname;
182 const char *zfile = NULL;
183 const cfg_obj_t *maps[4];
184 const cfg_obj_t *mastersobj = NULL;
185 const cfg_obj_t *inviewobj = NULL;
186 const cfg_obj_t *zoptions = NULL;
187 const cfg_obj_t *classobj = NULL;
188 const cfg_obj_t *typeobj = NULL;
189 const cfg_obj_t *fileobj = NULL;
190 const cfg_obj_t *dlzobj = NULL;
191 const cfg_obj_t *dbobj = NULL;
192 const cfg_obj_t *obj = NULL;
193 const cfg_obj_t *fmtobj = NULL;
194 dns_masterformat_t masterformat;
195 dns_ttl_t maxttl = 0;
196
197 zone_options = DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNS | DNS_ZONEOPT_MANYERRORS;
198
199 zname = cfg_obj_asstring(cfg_tuple_get(zconfig, "name"));
200 classobj = cfg_tuple_get(zconfig, "class");
201 if (!cfg_obj_isstring(classobj))
202 zclass = vclass;
203 else
204 zclass = cfg_obj_asstring(classobj);
205
206 zoptions = cfg_tuple_get(zconfig, "options");
207 maps[i++] = zoptions;
208 if (vconfig != NULL)
209 maps[i++] = cfg_tuple_get(vconfig, "options");
210 if (config != NULL) {
211 cfg_map_get(config, "options", &obj);
212 if (obj != NULL)
213 maps[i++] = obj;
214 }
215 maps[i] = NULL;
216
217 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "in-view", &inviewobj);
218 if (inviewobj != NULL && list) {
219 const char *inview = cfg_obj_asstring(inviewobj);
220 printf("%s %s %s in-view %s\n", zname, zclass, view, inview);
221 }
222 if (inviewobj != NULL)
223 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
224
225 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "type", &typeobj);
226 if (typeobj == NULL)
227 return (ISC_R_FAILURE);
228
229 if (list) {
230 const char *ztype = cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj);
231 printf("%s %s %s %s\n", zname, zclass, view, ztype);
232 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
233 }
234
235 /*
236 * Skip checks when using an alternate data source.
237 */
238 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "database", &dbobj);
239 if (dbobj != NULL &&
240 strcmp("rbt", cfg_obj_asstring(dbobj)) != 0 &&
241 strcmp("rbt64", cfg_obj_asstring(dbobj)) != 0)
242 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
243
244 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "dlz", &dlzobj);
245 if (dlzobj != NULL)
246 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
247
248 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "file", &fileobj);
249 if (fileobj != NULL)
250 zfile = cfg_obj_asstring(fileobj);
251
252 /*
253 * Check hints files for hint zones.
254 * Skip loading checks for any type other than
255 * master and redirect
256 */
257 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj), "hint") == 0) {
258 return (configure_hint(zfile, zclass, mctx));
259 } else if ((strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj), "primary") != 0) &&
260 (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj), "master") != 0) &&
261 (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj), "redirect") != 0))
262 {
263 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
264 }
265
266 /*
267 * Is the redirect zone configured as a slave?
268 */
269 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(typeobj), "redirect") == 0) {
270 cfg_map_get(zoptions, "masters", &mastersobj);
271 if (mastersobj != NULL)
272 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
273 }
274
275 if (zfile == NULL)
276 return (ISC_R_FAILURE);
277
278 obj = NULL;
279 if (get_maps(maps, "check-dup-records", &obj)) {
280 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
281 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRR;
282 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRRFAIL;
283 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "fail") == 0) {
284 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRR;
285 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRRFAIL;
286 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
287 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRR;
288 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRRFAIL;
289 } else {
290 INSIST(0);
291 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
292 }
293 } else {
294 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRR;
295 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKDUPRRFAIL;
296 }
297
298 obj = NULL;
299 if (get_maps(maps, "check-mx", &obj)) {
300 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
301 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMX;
302 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMXFAIL;
303 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "fail") == 0) {
304 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMX;
305 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMXFAIL;
306 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
307 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMX;
308 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMXFAIL;
309 } else {
310 INSIST(0);
311 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
312 }
313 } else {
314 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMX;
315 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKMXFAIL;
316 }
317
318 obj = NULL;
319 if (get_maps(maps, "check-integrity", &obj)) {
320 if (cfg_obj_asboolean(obj))
321 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKINTEGRITY;
322 else
323 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKINTEGRITY;
324 } else
325 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKINTEGRITY;
326
327 obj = NULL;
328 if (get_maps(maps, "check-mx-cname", &obj)) {
329 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
330 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNMXCNAME;
331 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNOREMXCNAME;
332 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "fail") == 0) {
333 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNMXCNAME;
334 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNOREMXCNAME;
335 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
336 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNMXCNAME;
337 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNOREMXCNAME;
338 } else {
339 INSIST(0);
340 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
341 }
342 } else {
343 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNMXCNAME;
344 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNOREMXCNAME;
345 }
346
347 obj = NULL;
348 if (get_maps(maps, "check-srv-cname", &obj)) {
349 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
350 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNSRVCNAME;
351 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNORESRVCNAME;
352 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "fail") == 0) {
353 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNSRVCNAME;
354 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNORESRVCNAME;
355 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
356 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNSRVCNAME;
357 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNORESRVCNAME;
358 } else {
359 INSIST(0);
360 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
361 }
362 } else {
363 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_WARNSRVCNAME;
364 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_IGNORESRVCNAME;
365 }
366
367 obj = NULL;
368 if (get_maps(maps, "check-sibling", &obj)) {
369 if (cfg_obj_asboolean(obj))
370 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKSIBLING;
371 else
372 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKSIBLING;
373 }
374
375 obj = NULL;
376 if (get_maps(maps, "check-spf", &obj)) {
377 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
378 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKSPF;
379 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
380 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKSPF;
381 } else {
382 INSIST(0);
383 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
384 }
385 } else {
386 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKSPF;
387 }
388
389 obj = NULL;
390 if (get_checknames(maps, &obj)) {
391 if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "warn") == 0) {
392 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMES;
393 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMESFAIL;
394 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "fail") == 0) {
395 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMES;
396 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMESFAIL;
397 } else if (strcasecmp(cfg_obj_asstring(obj), "ignore") == 0) {
398 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMES;
399 zone_options &= ~DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMESFAIL;
400 } else {
401 INSIST(0);
402 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
403 }
404 } else {
405 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMES;
406 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKNAMESFAIL;
407 }
408
409 masterformat = dns_masterformat_text;
410 fmtobj = NULL;
411 if (get_maps(maps, "masterfile-format", &fmtobj)) {
412 const char *masterformatstr = cfg_obj_asstring(fmtobj);
413 if (strcasecmp(masterformatstr, "text") == 0) {
414 masterformat = dns_masterformat_text;
415 } else if (strcasecmp(masterformatstr, "raw") == 0) {
416 masterformat = dns_masterformat_raw;
417 } else if (strcasecmp(masterformatstr, "map") == 0) {
418 masterformat = dns_masterformat_map;
419 } else {
420 INSIST(0);
421 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
422 }
423 }
424
425 obj = NULL;
426 if (get_maps(maps, "max-zone-ttl", &obj)) {
427 maxttl = cfg_obj_asuint32(obj);
428 zone_options |= DNS_ZONEOPT_CHECKTTL;
429 }
430
431 result = load_zone(mctx, zname, zfile, masterformat,
432 zclass, maxttl, NULL);
433 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
434 fprintf(stderr, "%s/%s/%s: %s\n", view, zname, zclass,
435 dns_result_totext(result));
436 return (result);
437}

439/*% configure a view */
440static isc_result_t
441configure_view(const char *vclass, const char *view, const cfg_obj_t *config,
442 const cfg_obj_t *vconfig, isc_mem_t *mctx, bool list)
443{
444 const cfg_listelt_t *element;
445 const cfg_obj_t *voptions;
446 const cfg_obj_t *zonelist;
447 isc_result_t result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
448 isc_result_t tresult;
449
450 voptions = NULL;
451 if (vconfig != NULL)
452 voptions = cfg_tuple_get(vconfig, "options");
453
454 zonelist = NULL;
455 if (voptions != NULL)
456 (void)cfg_map_get(voptions, "zone", &zonelist);
457 else
458 (void)cfg_map_get(config, "zone", &zonelist);
459
460 for (element = cfg_list_first(zonelist);
461 element != NULL;
462 element = cfg_list_next(element))
463 {
464 const cfg_obj_t *zconfig = cfg_listelt_value(element);
465 tresult = configure_zone(vclass, view, zconfig, vconfig,
466 config, mctx, list);
467 if (tresult != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
468 result = tresult;
469 }
470 return (result);
471}
472
473static isc_result_t
474config_getclass(const cfg_obj_t *classobj, dns_rdataclass_t defclass,
475 dns_rdataclass_t *classp)
476{
477 isc_textregion_t r;
478
479 if (!cfg_obj_isstring(classobj)) {
480 *classp = defclass;
481 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
482 }
483 DE_CONST(cfg_obj_asstring(classobj), r.base);
484 r.length = strlen(r.base);
485 return (dns_rdataclass_fromtext(classp, &r));
486}
487
488/*% load zones from the configuration */
489static isc_result_t
490load_zones_fromconfig(const cfg_obj_t *config, isc_mem_t *mctx,
491 bool list_zones)
492{
493 const cfg_listelt_t *element;
494 const cfg_obj_t *views;
495 const cfg_obj_t *vconfig;
496 isc_result_t result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
497 isc_result_t tresult;
498
499 views = NULL;
500
501 (void)cfg_map_get(config, "view", &views);
502 for (element = cfg_list_first(views);
503 element != NULL;
504 element = cfg_list_next(element))
505 {
506 const cfg_obj_t *classobj;
507 dns_rdataclass_t viewclass;
508 const char *vname;
509 char buf[sizeof("CLASS65535")];
510
511 vconfig = cfg_listelt_value(element);
512 if (vconfig == NULL)
513 continue;
514
515 classobj = cfg_tuple_get(vconfig, "class");
516 CHECK(config_getclass(classobj, dns_rdataclass_in,
517 &viewclass));
518 if (dns_rdataclass_ismeta(viewclass))
519 CHECK(ISC_R_FAILURE);
520
521 dns_rdataclass_format(viewclass, buf, sizeof(buf));
522 vname = cfg_obj_asstring(cfg_tuple_get(vconfig, "name"));
523 tresult = configure_view(buf, vname, config, vconfig, mctx,
524 list_zones);
525 if (tresult != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
526 result = tresult;
527 }
528
529 if (views == NULL) {
530 tresult = configure_view("IN", "_default", config, NULL, mctx,
531 list_zones);
532 if (tresult != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
533 result = tresult;
534 }
535
536cleanup:
537 return (result);
538}
539
540static void
541output(void *closure, const char *text, int textlen) {
542 UNUSED(closure);
543 if (fwrite(text, 1, textlen, stdout) != (size_t)textlen) {
544 perror("fwrite");
545 exit(1);
546 }
547}
548
549/*% The main processing routine */
550int
551main(int argc, char **argv) {
552 int c;
553 cfg_parser_t *parser = NULL;
554 cfg_obj_t *config = NULL;
555 const char *conffile = NULL;
556 isc_mem_t *mctx = NULL;
557 isc_result_t result;
558 int exit_status = 0;
559 bool load_zones = false;
560 bool list_zones = false;
561 bool print = false;
562 unsigned int flags = 0;
563
564 isc_commandline_errprint = false;
565
566 /*
567 * Process memory debugging argument first.
568 */
569#define CMDLINE_FLAGS "cdhjlm:t:pvxz"
570 while ((c = isc_commandline_parse(argc, argv, CMDLINE_FLAGS)) != -1) {
571 switch (c) {
572 case 'm':
573 if (strcasecmp(isc_commandline_argument, "record") == 0)
574 isc_mem_debugging |= ISC_MEM_DEBUGRECORD;
575 if (strcasecmp(isc_commandline_argument, "trace") == 0)
576 isc_mem_debugging |= ISC_MEM_DEBUGTRACE;
577 if (strcasecmp(isc_commandline_argument, "usage") == 0)
578 isc_mem_debugging |= ISC_MEM_DEBUGUSAGE;
579 if (strcasecmp(isc_commandline_argument, "size") == 0)
580 isc_mem_debugging |= ISC_MEM_DEBUGSIZE;
581 if (strcasecmp(isc_commandline_argument, "mctx") == 0)
582 isc_mem_debugging |= ISC_MEM_DEBUGCTX;
583 break;
584 default:
585 break;
586 }
587 }
588 isc_commandline_reset = true;
589
590 RUNTIME_CHECK(isc_mem_create(0, 0, &mctx) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
591
592 while ((c = isc_commandline_parse(argc, argv, CMDLINE_FLAGS)) != EOF) {
593 switch (c) {
594 case 'c':
595 loadplugins = false;
596 break;
597
598 case 'd':
599 debug++;
600 break;
601
602 case 'j':
603 nomerge = false;
604 break;
605
606 case 'l':
607 list_zones = true;
608 break;
609
610 case 'm':
611 break;
612
613 case 't':
614 result = isc_dir_chroot(isc_commandline_argument);
615 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
616 fprintf(stderr, "isc_dir_chroot: %s\n",
617 isc_result_totext(result));
618 exit(1);
619 }
620 break;
621
622 case 'p':
623 print = true;
624 break;
625
626 case 'v':
627 printf(VERSION "\n");
628 exit(0);
629
630 case 'x':
631 flags |= CFG_PRINTER_XKEY;
632 break;
633
634 case 'z':
635 load_zones = true;
636 docheckmx = false;
637 docheckns = false;
638 dochecksrv = false;
639 break;
640
641 case '?':
642 if (isc_commandline_option != '?')
643 fprintf(stderr, "%s: invalid argument -%c\n",
644 program, isc_commandline_option);
645 /* FALLTHROUGH */
646 case 'h':
647 usage();
648
649 default:
650 fprintf(stderr, "%s: unhandled option -%c\n",
651 program, isc_commandline_option);
652 exit(1);
653 }
654 }
655
656 if (((flags & CFG_PRINTER_XKEY) != 0) && !print) {
657 fprintf(stderr, "%s: -x cannot be used without -p\n", program);
658 exit(1);
659 }
660 if (print && list_zones) {
661 fprintf(stderr, "%s: -l cannot be used with -p\n", program);
662 exit(1);
663 }
664
665 if (isc_commandline_index + 1 < argc)
666 usage();
667 if (argv[isc_commandline_index] != NULL)
668 conffile = argv[isc_commandline_index];
669 if (conffile == NULL || conffile[0] == '\0')
670 conffile = NAMED_CONFFILE;
671
672#ifdef _WIN32
673 InitSockets();
674#endif
675
676 RUNTIME_CHECK(setup_logging(mctx, stdout, &logc) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
677
678 dns_result_register();
679
680 RUNTIME_CHECK(cfg_parser_create(mctx, logc, &parser) == ISC_R_SUCCESS);
681
682 cfg_parser_setcallback(parser, directory_callback, NULL);
683
684 if (cfg_parse_file(parser, conffile, &cfg_type_namedconf, &config) !=
685 ISC_R_SUCCESS)
686 exit(1);
687
688 result = bind9_check_namedconf(config, loadplugins, logc, mctx);
689 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
690 exit_status = 1;
691 }
692
693 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS && (load_zones || list_zones)) {
694 result = load_zones_fromconfig(config, mctx, list_zones);
695 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
696 exit_status = 1;
697 }
698
699 if (print && exit_status == 0)
700 cfg_printx(config, flags, output, NULL);
701 cfg_obj_destroy(parser, &config);
702
703 cfg_parser_destroy(&parser);
704
705 dns_name_destroy();
706
707 isc_log_destroy(&logc);
708
709 isc_mem_destroy(&mctx);
710
711#ifdef _WIN32
712 DestroySockets();
713#endif
714
715 return (exit_status);
716}
